text: Arthur Gravel (born 1905, date of death unknown) was a Canadian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Canadian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Canada Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal
